   Événements / Irak / Journée d'étude
       02/10/2019

Rencontre : Archaeological Research in Iraqi Kurdistan (10/10/2019)
       This Rencontre, organized by the General Directorate of Antiquities
       in Kurdistan and the Ifpo, aims at gathering the archaeological
       teams currently on the field in order to present their latest
       results. Download the program Date and time Thursday October 10,
       2019, 8 am – 6:30 pm Location Training Center of the GDA (see plan
       attached to the program) Contact and information Reservation at
       contact.irak@ifporient.org https://www.facebook.com/ifpoerbil/
       Lecture...
